<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.6">
<l>maṭaleṭutta neṭuntāḻai maruṅkellām vaḷarpavaḷam</l>
<l>tiṭaleṭuttuc cuṭarimaikkun tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>aṭalaṭarttaṉ ṟiraṇiyaṉai muraṇaḻiya vaṇiyukirāl</l>
<l>uṭaleṭutta perumāṉuk kiḻantēṉe ṉoḷivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my bright bangles to the great lord who once lifted with his lovely claws</l>
<l>The body of Hiraṇya, crushing his power so [his] opposition failed,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram where corals, which appear at all sides</l>
<l>Of tall screwpine bearing flat leaves, [and] being high on the dunes,</l>
<l rend="indent">twinkle with light.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
